snippet.title: Let's VR: OMEGA AGENT - Gear VR gameplay
snippet.description: In Omega Agent for Gear VR, I'm a secret agent... with a jetpack. Join me in my airborn mission to explore and defend Omega Island in this adventure by Fireproof Games. Part of my series Let's VR: virtual reality gameplay videos. Subscribe for Gear VR game reviews, walkthroughs, and tips: youtube.com/amberVR
